org.apache.flink.util

类 ReflectionUtil.FullTypeInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.util.ReflectionUtil.FullTypeInfo
  • 封闭类:
    ReflectionUtil

    public static class ReflectionUtil.FullTypeInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    Container for the full type information of a type. This means that it contains the Class object and for each template parameter it contains a full type information describing the type.
